955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"浪費共雪網路資源<br />\n<br />\n又係dps 又係sup 嘅bbr. 今季第一次有<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TWRLgMDrpJI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTWRLgMDrpJI&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV093lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=c3e7fad7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TWRLgMDrpJI</a>"},{"pid":"cab8f6408816bc903692ee23fc4fd2e54d599dde","tid":1756955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T09:20:55.000Z","msg":"共雪最新作品D4 新update<br />\n資料量頗大<br />\n<a href=\"https://us.diablo3.com/en/blog/23230076/system-design-in-diablo-iv-part-ii-12-3-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fus.diablo3.com%2Fen%2Fblog%2F23230076%2Fsystem-design-in-diablo-iv-part-ii-12-3-2019&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV093lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=4e0ca5ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://us.diablo3.com/en/blog/23230076/system-design-in-diablo-iv-part-ii-12-3-2019</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0: 新任Game designer 會由韓仔擔任，本身亦曾經係幾季world solo 同world 4人嘅champion，對D3 有非常清楚嘅認知，難怪今季為D3歷年來最好玩既季。<br />\n<br />\n1: 取消遠古item, 當然亦會同時取消unique item，製作團隊指為了道具嘅多樣性，而unique power 側會好似Kanni cube 咁用鑄造形式加上<br />\n<br />\n2: 仍然會吸收D3 最高階嘅幾項core skills （指player skills, 如monsters &amp; pyrons management, snapslot damage, coe rotate）為D4 技術主軸，但不會令到D4 同D3/D2 有非常類似嘅系統。這將會係製作團隊最大嘅一項挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n4: Affix 會更清楚地分成三項： Buff/Debuff/on-hit effect, 亦係D3 一貫嘅affix 設計（尤其set item), 而升level時可供用家加points,  如夠points 先會發動item affix power. <br />\n<br />\n5: 佢地想改變攻擊同防禦成日要用成身item相互間扶持既情況，認同大家都想攻擊力由武器決定，防禦由防具決定嘅做法。但佢地同時想避免你一拎起某件大數字武防就突然變勁呢種做法，有如同D3<br />\n<br />\n6: Paragon 正在討論當中， 團隊討論頗烈，未決定到是否cap鳩佢地。"},{"pid":"f52ed36fbb9a74106cf7088c09663a4d0c7ee9ba","tid":1756955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"漏夜趕科場嘅當代最強D3  player 之一<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCs20qCPrd1AXRviSTdVCoAg/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCs20qCPrd1AXRviSTdVCoAg%2Fvideos&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV093lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=9ca19808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCs20qCPrd1AXRviSTdVCoAg/videos</a>"},{"pid":"e01f27752d28e47b5f0df460ed5592245d8809d1","tid":1756955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:02:06.000Z","msg":"GR 150 speedrun<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FKTvozwV4iY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFKTvozwV4iY&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV093lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=460e8ca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FKTvozwV4iY</a>"},{"pid":"cfed61f11f81fe8747a0ae4780dd01ea4c5576b6","tid":1756955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"繼續係冇人睇既今季地圖衝層攻略<br />\n我會試下慨括晒冇法師既速刷同衝層方式<br />\n<br />\n今季主軸變成用Seasonal Bonus 殺怪，甚至係殺RG為主<br />\n<br />\nplv裝備顯得不再重要，轉而代之最重要係技術仲有運氣<br />\n如何喺200 隻高層怪之間生存將成為重要課題<br />\n<br />\nwudijo過150 時只得不完美嘅裝備，120 打卡同2000plv<br />\n<br />\n各連殺用法<br />\n15 - 一個全畫面攻擊，所有小怪會死<br />\n30 - 一個frost nova， 半血中型怪會死<br />\n50 - 跌屍體，大慨可扣藍怪33% 血，中小怪即死，大怪減半<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />15-50 呢三個Bonus 一般會一次過發動，理論上白怪都會死晒<br />\n<br />\n100 - 威力強大但不可控嘅龍卷風，會以有幾多個風車中怪物計算，首次觸及扣一半，第二次觸及80%，第三次觸及即死。傷害比例，係不論藍黃，甚至不論RG的。<br />\n<br />\n150 - 一個為時2 秒嘅地雷，觸及怪物即死，RG同由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />100 同150 特點在於難操控但威力強大，都係即死級，但又相當難擊中你既心儀怪物，故此只要控得好100 同150， 可得天下。100 風的話，玩過第5季風法應該會識，就係盡量喺窄位，或牆角觸發。然後用拉怪技能引怪食風，總之100 風proc時重點並不是輸出，而係引怪。150 炸彈則是貼近你既精英怪觸發，因為你嘅攻擊目標會被引起地雷。<br />\n<br />\n200 - 落寶箱，落寶箱同樣有技術，窄位使用可令箱落晒去同一點，運氣好的話足夠殺藍黃。<br />\n<br />\n300 - Fire wing，所有被擊中怪物扣50% 血，包括RG。但總體上係廢既<br />\n<br />\n400 - 核爆，所有怪死晒<br />\n<br />\n500 - 召喚天使，任何單體五刀死，今季嘅RG KILLER<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />- 一般而言，200 目的係觸發大量殺怪至300多，故此如果普通衝層，只會靚圖先使用。否則，不斷咁100-150 已經夠。而400 則是你喺200之後見靚cond，然後一下觸發至超過400 為主。所以總括而言，衝層時，發動得400 表示你本身已經打得好順。<br />\n<br />\n500 係當你極限衝層時用，詳情google wudijo，在此不多詳述"},{"pid":"e7e56ecb40be9739496b2e6bb18b3ff9e8fcffb7","tid":1756955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:17:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/84EwtxA4mes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F84EwtxA4mes&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV093lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=0b259c6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/84EwtxA4mes</a><br />\n<br />\nincase 有人想知"},{"pid":"21dfbebe4265b733bea1865f79a3685f13bf641b","tid":1756955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:22:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b6JsNX_y4iA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb6JsNX_y4iA&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV093lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=889adceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b6JsNX_y4iA</a>"},{"pid":"52d1076c96d7dace6bb6ffb616954c53f23fa41e","tid":1756955,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"仲有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2955feb0dc05dc845eee9dc825bfc5a51f57551b","tid":1756955,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d1076c96d7dace6bb6ffb616954c53f23fa41e","tid":1756955,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T19:04:53.000Z","msg":"仲有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"今季應該係19季來出得最好嘅一季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純技術+唔駛咁多運氣"},{"pid":"b97fedfa64d92957fc2cc5f9f37659edab9ba444","tid":175695